<div id="risk" class="page-break">
  <h1>Risk Assessment</h1>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Understanding and managing risk is crucial for retirement success. This section analyzes key risk factors that could impact your financial security.</p>
    
    <h2 id="risk-market">Market Risk</h2>
    
    <table class="avoid-break" aria-label="Market risk factors and mitigations">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Risk Factor</th>
          <th>Current Assumption</th>
          <th>Impact Level</th>
          <th>Mitigation Strategy</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Return Volatility</td>
          <td>Ïƒ = {{formatPercent assumptions.roiStdev 1}}</td>
          <td>High</td>
          <td>Diversification across asset classes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Sequence of Returns</td>
          <td>Monte Carlo modeled</td>
          <td>High</td>
          <td>Flexible withdrawal strategy</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Inflation Erosion</td>
          <td>{{formatPercent assumptions.inflationMean 1}} mean</td>
          <td>Medium</td>
          <td>Real asset allocation</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Currency Risk</td>
          <td>EUR-denominated</td>
          <td>Low</td>
          <td>Local currency focus</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <h2 id="risk-longevity">Longevity Risk</h2>
    
    <div class="callout callout-info">
      <div class="callout-title">Planning Horizon Analysis</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Current planning horizon: Age {{person.horizonAge}} ({{subtract person.horizonAge person.currentAge}} years)</li>
        <li>Years in retirement: {{subtract person.horizonAge person.retireAge}}</li>
        <li>Risk of outliving assets: {{formatPercent (subtract 100 projections.successRatePct)}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <h2 id="risk-scenarios">Scenario Analysis</h2>
    
    <h3 id="risk-stress">Stress Test Results</h3>
    
    <table class="avoid-break" aria-label="Stress test scenarios and impacts">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Scenario</th>
          <th>Portfolio Impact</th>
          <th>Success Rate Impact</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Base Case</td>
          <td>As projected</td>
          <td>{{formatPercent projections.successRatePct}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>High Inflation (+2%)</td>
          <td>-15% real value</td>
          <td>~{{formatPercent (subtract projections.successRatePct 10)}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Low Returns (-2%)</td>
          <td>-25% terminal value</td>
          <td>~{{formatPercent (subtract projections.successRatePct 15)}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Extended Longevity (+5 years)</td>
          <td>Additional withdrawals</td>
          <td>~{{formatPercent (subtract projections.successRatePct 8)}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <h2 id="risk-mitigation">Risk Mitigation Strategies</h2>
    
    <div class="kpi-grid">
      {{> kpi-tile 
        value="Diversify"
        label="Investment Strategy"
        note="Spread risk across multiple asset classes and geographies"
      }}
      
      {{> kpi-tile 
        value="Flexible"
        label="Spending Approach"
        note="Adjust withdrawals based on market conditions"
      }}
      
      {{> kpi-tile 
        value="Buffer"
        label="Safety Margin"
        note="Maintain emergency reserves for market downturns"
      }}
      
      {{> kpi-tile 
        value="Review"
        label="Regular Assessment"
        note="Annual portfolio and assumption reviews"
      }}
    </div>
    
    <h2 id="risk-indicators">Key Risk Indicators</h2>
    
    <div class="callout callout-warning">
      <div class="callout-title">Warning Signals to Monitor</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Portfolio value falls below P10 projection for your age</li>
        <li>Annual spending exceeds 5% of portfolio value</li>
        <li>Inflation persistently exceeds {{formatPercent (multiply assumptions.inflationMean 1.5)}} </li>
        <li>Investment returns lag assumptions for 3+ consecutive years</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
